\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
t_{w}\left(\frac{1}{2^{n}}\right)=\frac{1}{2^{n-1}}\;\frac{1-2^{n}w^{n}}{1-2w}\label{eq:}\end{equation}

\end_inset 

 which is a polynomial of finite degree, without any poles (there is no
